  "reference_number": "RUS1099",
  "remarks": "\nGalina Danilchenko is the ‘acting mayor’ of Melitopol, installed by Russian military forces in temporary control of Ukrainian territory. Danilchenko has provided support for and promoted policies and actions that threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, including through endorsing and acting in support of Russian occupation of Melitopol as part of efforts to normalise and provide legitimacy to it.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
